text: The 2015 All Ireland Ladies' Club Football Championship was the 39th edition of the All-Ireland Ladies' Club Football Championship. Donaghmoyne (Monaghan) won the title after defeating Mourneabbey by 0-11 to 0-8 in the final. ==Qualification== ==Results== ===All Ireland Ladies' Club Football Championship=== ==References== 2015 Club
